    <h1>Pancakes</h1>

    <img src="https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/pancakes-pancake.jpg" alt="Fluffy Pancakes" width="400">

    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>These pancakes are fluffy and perfect for a weekend breakfast.</p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Flour</li>
        <li>Milk</li>
        <li>Eggs</li>
        <li>Sugar</li>
        <li>Baking powder</li>
        <li>Butter</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Mix dry ingredients together.</li>
        <li>Whisk wet ingredients and combine with dry mixture.</li>
        <li>Heat a pan and pour batter.</li>
        <li>Cook until bubbles form, then flip.</li>
        <li>Serve warm with syrup.</li>
    </ol>
